[Name] GLib
[Summary] HexChat is an IRC client based on XChat.
[Description] HexChat is an IRC client based on XChat, but unlike XChat it’s completely free for both Windows and Unix-like systems. Since XChat is open source, it’s perfectly legal.
[License] GNU General Public License version 2 (or later)
[Homepage] https://hexchat.github.io/index.html
